Some nice characters for UI dev:

>> Single Line Characters:
Horizontal line: ─
Vertical line: │
Top-left corner: ┌
Top-right corner: ┐
Bottom-left corner: └
Bottom-right corner: ┘
T-junctions:
    Left: ├
    Right: ┤
    Top: ┬
    Bottom: ┴
    Cross: ┼

>> Double Line Characters:
Horizontal line: ═
Vertical line: ║
Top-left corner: ╔
Top-right corner: ╗
Bottom-left corner: ╚
Bottom-right corner: ╝
T-junctions:
    Left: ╠
    Right: ╣
    Top: ╦
    Bottom: ╩
    Cross: ╬

>> Block Characters:
Full block: █
Light shade: ░
Medium shade: ▒
Dark shade: ▓